					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1257738#post-2325350</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1257738/the-playful-beast#post-2325350</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2015 09:07:28 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>TobiasTheTapir</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1980552</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The girl is not modeled after any specific character, she is more like a generic tsundere. Given that Asuka is one of my favorite anime characters, you can say that she's inspired in part by her. I haven't seen the new Dragon Ball movie yet. I used Kamehameha as the final attack because it is well-known even among those who are not anime fans. The Spirit Bomb could work as well, but I think that it is a little less known. The other attacks mentioned only serve a decorative purpose, so it's okay if the reader never heard of them before.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
